    "title": "Changes to support for people displaced from Ukraine in Poland",
    "link": "https://home-affairs.ec.europa.eu/news/changes-support-people-displaced-ukraine-poland-2026-03-26_en",
    "pubDate": "2026-03-26T15:29:20.000Z",
    "content": "<p>The Polish government drafted an official act to phase out measures introduced in 2022 to support people displaced from Ukraine by the ongoing war. Following a transitional period, beneficiaries of temporary protection would face reduced access to some family benefits, healthcare, and accommodation.</p>",
